title: Ep. #50 | Amber Liu Takeover: f(x) Solo Playlist
description:
This week’s guest host is none other than…. Amber Liu! While Eric’s away in L.A., Amber is here to highlight her favorite f(x) solo songs. Amber also shares some special stories and lessons learnt from each of the f(x) members. Want to have your questions answered by future guests like Amber? Make sure to submit questions on DIVE Studios' Discord server!
Make sure to subscribe to @daebakshow (IT’S FREE) and leave a comment, rating and/or review on Spotify, Apple Podcasts, Soundcloud, and YouTube.
Episodes are presented by @thedivestudios
Connect with us on all social media platforms @daebakshow and at http://www.divestudios.io/daebakshow !
